      "span_text": "The nucleotide sequence data reported are available in the GenBank databases. The NCBI, Seattle SNPs and ENCODE web sites were searched for previously reported CD24L4 and DDX3Y mutations. Also, the 236 resequenced (accession codes BV678971-BV679207) PCR fragments by Repping et al. [CITATION_3] were aligned and examined for DDX3Y region nucleotide changes."
